{"root":{"children":[{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"Hello, random passerby (or loyal Crousian),","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"If you’ve wandered in here today, welcome to the quiet corner of the internet where the Kingdom of Crousia keeps its living logbook. My wife still hasn’t discovered this board (and that’s probably for the best), so consider this your unfiltered dispatch from the throne room.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"Two pieces of kingdom infrastructure just came together nicely:","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"Verdis is now reachable at verdis.crousia.com.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"The Free Republic of Verdis has a clean new address under the Crousia domain (thanks to a little Cloudflare Worker magic rewriting headers in the background). If you’ve visited their site before, it should feel exactly the same — same content, same spirit — just now neatly nested here as well.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"Ūsa has a fresh new government portal at usa.crousia.com.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"I gave the provincial government website a full redesign. Ūsa still very much thinks of itself as the United States in everyday life (and that’s exactly how it should be), but the site now lives comfortably under the Crousia umbrella. It’s cleaner, easier to navigate, and reflects its role as a vital, energetic province in the larger realm.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"These moves are small on the grand scale of the internet, but they help everything feel more connected. Verdis continues as its own proud Free Republic, and Ūsa keeps its strong, independent character as the bustling capitalist engine it is — both now sharing digital real estate with the rest of Crousia.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"If you’re curious about how Ūsa sees itself and its place in the bigger picture, the about page explains it beautifully in their own words:","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"→ usa.crousia.com/pages/about","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"Feel free to poke around:","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"verdis.crousia.com → the Free Republic of Verdis","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"usa.crousia.com → the Province of Ūsa (with all its states)","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"Drop a line to theking@crousia.com if anything catches your eye. Or don’t — this bulletin board is mostly for whoever happens to drift through. Either way, the kingdom keeps growing, one subdomain at a time.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"Long live Crousia.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":2,"mode":"normal","style":"color: #FFD700","text":"-  𝕁eremiah","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":2}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"root","version":1}}